nodes.text: 6369 was a B1-series battle droid that served in the Trade Federation Droid Army. During the Naboo Crisis, 6369 was assigned to guard the entrance to the Theed Royal Palace throne room.
The B1's designation was written on the back of his comlink booster pack.

6369 first appeared in the 1999 film Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, the first installment of the Star Wars prequel trilogy. While the droid's designation can be spotted in film, the numbers could not be identified until Star Wars: The Complete Visual Dictionary, New Edition gave a translation for B1 numerals.
